comments.body:
[~elgoiri], corrected the indentation in patch v2. Test itself seems slow as it has wait and retry logic at many steps. Since we are using default EC policy 6,3 we are running 9 node minidfs cluster so cluster setup & teardown in every iteration seems add to this overhead. 
{quote}I'm specially curious why the buffer went from 1k to 2k.{quote}
I was experimenting to see if it can reduces test runtime. On a second thought this seems unnecessary and doesn't really improve runtime. Changed it back to 1024 in v2.
